analysisPopulations.name: Screened Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.label: Screened
analysisPopulations.description: All participants who have signed informed consent(s)

analysisPopulations.name: All Enrolled Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.label: All Enrolled
analysisPopulations.description: All participants who are enrolled (as defined in Section 5.6 of the protocol) in the study

analysisPopulations.name: Full Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.label: FAS
analysisPopulations.description: All participants who are enrolled in the study, have received at least 1 dose of study drug, and have at least 1 valid postbaseline assessment
analysisPopulations.criteria: Enrolled, received at least 1 dose of study drug, and have at least 1 valid postbaseline assessment

analysisPopulations.name: Per-Protocol Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.label: PPAS
analysisPopulations.description: A subset of the FAS and will include all participants who did not have any important protocol deviations affecting the efficacy evaluations
analysisPopulations.criteria: FAS participants without important protocol deviations affecting efficacy evaluations

analysisPopulations.name: Safety Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.label: Safety
analysisPopulations.description: All participants who are enrolled in the study and have received at least 1 dose of study drug
analysisPopulations.criteria: Enrolled and received at least 1 dose of study drug

analysisPopulations.name: Pharmacokinetic Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.label: PK
analysisPopulations.description: All participants in the safety analysis set who have at least 1 evaluable postdose PK concentration value
analysisPopulations.criteria: Safety analysis set participants with at least 1 evaluable postdose PK concentration value
